{"tid":1788532,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"彩瑛炫耀超正媽媽　鵝蛋臉露甜笑「美貌神複製」","createTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T13:05:42.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c339cc70cb1027dcf8530dbf202ea037381dba95","tid":1788532,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cnca59SUIAAJYlb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCnca59SUIAAJYlb.jpg&h=5190d544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夯團 9人各具特色魅力，成員家族基因獲得外界認證，除了「超正姊妹花」定延跟姊姊昇延、Mina與子瑜的母親，彩瑛也在IG炫耀，自豪「我媽媽太漂亮了」，決定PO出影片與大家分享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/z5ezkXx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fz5ezkXx.gif&h=e29fde81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1754bee374896335fa3dfe0dd5bbb6101a3ea73","tid":1788532,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"彩瑛在IG上傳5張照片，張張造型多變，她表示：「我喜歡特別又有趣的髮型！」此外加碼PO出一支跟弟弟為母親慶生的影片，寫下：「最後是不久前媽媽生日的影片，因為太漂亮了，想要炫耀決定上傳！」獲得大批粉絲生日祝福，以及稱讚媽媽真的很美。"},{"pid":"5e83c0f85e763f77cffb1d33484e3076ce8d8563","tid":1788532,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://koreaboo-cdn.storage.googleapis.com/2017/09/chaeyoung1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkoreaboo-cdn.storage.googleapis.com%2F2017%2F09%2Fchaeyoung1.jpg&h=547084e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dz5aflDUwAAkjEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDz5aflDUwAAkjEL.jpg&h=81b370c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b1b157c6a3c8936958880367ff34f5808e2a291","tid":1788532,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"各成員美貌也是獲得國際認證，每年的最美臉孔榜單大家皆入圍，而子瑜更蟬聯「亞洲最美」寶座，今年她也在提名名單上，是否再抱走美名備受期待。"},{"pid":"ac1ab413beb7a0f2f7da93e5582c961d3e7cb792","tid":1788532,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:45:20.000Z","msg":"好普通咋喎<br />\n同埋明明係方形臉"},{"pid":"11fa34b8d270abd2f8e053385e070ca2f2fbc02f","tid":1788532,"uid":255926,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3TX0Ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3TX0Ee.jpg&h=32c94e81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5uDK5X.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5uDK5X.gif&h=5af616f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sG40YqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsG40YqY.jpg&h=d4bb612b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩瑛真係好靚。。。"},{"pid":"3496e1072bf09cc2545bc32666631c31c9f0231d","tid":1788532,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稅局行動宣言：<br />\n<br />\n稅局，納稅人金錢吐納之處。六月以降，香港警隊搬出大量催淚彈、布袋彈、橡膠子彈甚或實彈，一一射向香港市民。購置武器，所費不菲，警隊資金何來？稅款必是一大來源。港人金錢，變作供養濫暴警隊的薪水，變作不人道武器還於港人之身，這絕非稅款的正當用途。政府無能，特首執拗難以平息民憤，何解需公帑埋單？<br />\n<br />\n香港市民安分守己，繳納血汗金錢；今民意所指為五大訴求，政府乃人民公僕，理應善用公帑以平眾怒，藉稅款促進訴求之達成以撫民心。然林鄭政府恣意調用港人金錢，屢行政治操作，維護腐敗議會，投稅款入朽壞警隊之血海，廣大市民如何甘心將夙夜辛勞所得，雙手奉上予這毫無公信力的政府？<br />\n<br />\n我等市民將一連三星期到稅局抗議，以示港人之怒，不到五大訴求悉數落實一日不熄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=fec13a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6tg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=cb7e12f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"06f954e8f7ae22dabd32efa2f3eb5c24e88b3db7","tid":1788532,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:13:44.000Z","msg":"人美心善"},{"pid":"8068256c4f89e1322cf70dd70a23f479fbff186b","tid":1788532,"uid":555,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"朴彩英好似正啲"},{"pid":"c36a274832093be5028387874a2c34391046ad0b","tid":1788532,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:21:57.000Z","msg":"哇呢個女仔幾可愛"},{"pid":"b76ad5af5231541c092329fedb3346af272ed341","tid":1788532,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2339/2339827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2339%2F2339827.jpg&h=196b1330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個牙隱正好多"},{"pid":"70b9d47dcae6be87ca2ba7fb06c933373ea8351c","tid":1788532,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"正....有種無形嘅吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ce6b6291a0d3b4b2c78e1f8372f27aa2d6222f","tid":1788532,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b76ad5af5231541c092329fedb3346af272ed341","tid":1788532,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2339/2339827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2339%2F2339827.jpg&h=196b1330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個牙隱正好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dislike.gif\" clas